.lq-progress-box{
display: none;
}
</code></pre> Change the styles of the choices <pre><code>/* Change the styles of the choices */
li.lq-choice, li.lq-choice{
/* your CSS rules go here */
}
</code></pre> Change the styles of the picture choices <pre><code>.lq-images li.lq-choice, .lq-images li.lq-choice{
/* your CSS rules go here */
}
</code></pre> Place the footer bar at the top, for more visibility <pre><code>.lq-footer, .lq-footer{
