{{/eq}}
{{/each}}
</code></pre></p> </li> <li> <p>List recommended products separated by Slot Blocks: If you want to recommend a Morning and Night slot routine separately you can use the following code. Make sure to change the block IDs (“A4TeY9” and “PPT2PG”) to the ones in your quiz.     <pre><code>&lt;h3&gt;Let’s start with your morning routine&lt;/h3&gt;
